Titolo: The Legend of Spyro: Dawn of the Dragon

Anno: 2008

Descrizione: The Legend of Spyro: Dawn of the Dragon is an action-adventure video game which is the third and final installment in The Legend of Spyro trilogy, as well as the tenth anniversary game of the series. It was developed by Ã‰tranges Libellules, as opposed to Krome Studios, and published by Activision in North America and Vivendi Games in the PAL Regions for the PlayStation 2, PlayStation 3, Xbox 360 and Wii.
Tantalus Media developed the Nintendo DS version. It is the end of the second Spyro continuity, with Skylanders: Spyro's Adventure serving as the second reboot of the franchise after Sierra Entertainment's parent company Vivendi Games merged with video game publisher Activision to form the Activision Blizzard holding company on July 10, 2008.

Genere: Action-adventure 

